Notes & Reminders Mobile App — Release Notes
Version 1.0.0 (Initial Release)
Release Date: November 7, 2025

Overview
Introducing the Notes & Reminders App, your all-in-one mobile companion for capturing ideas, organizing tasks, and setting smart reminders — anytime, anywhere. Designed for simplicity, speed, and productivity.

New Features

Create & Manage Notes
•	Quickly add, edit, and delete text notes.
•	Each note can include titles, content, and color labels for easy organization.
•	Autosave ensures your thoughts are never lost.

Set Smart Reminders
•	Add one-time or recurring reminders to any note.
•	Get push notifications even when the app is closed.
•	Snooze reminders or mark tasks as completed directly from the notification.

Powerful Search & Filters
•	Instantly search notes by title or keywords.
•	Filter by tags, categories, or reminder status.

Categories & Tags
•	Organize notes by custom folders or tags.
•	Keep personal, work, and study notes neatly separated.

Clean & Modern Interface
•	Minimalist design for distraction-free note-taking.
•	Optimized for both light and dark modes.
•	Smooth navigation and quick animations.

Notification System
•	Receive reliable local reminders for your notes.
•	Customize alert tones, vibration patterns, and notification times.

Performance & Stability
•	Improved startup speed and memory efficiency.
•	Optimized background scheduling for low battery impact.
•	Enhanced offline performance with local database storage.

Known Issues
•	Occasional minor delay in reminder notifications on some Android versions.
•	Sorting preferences may reset after app restart on certain devices.

Coming Soon (v1.1)
•	Cloud backup & sync with Google Drive / iCloud
•	Voice notes with speech-to-text
•	Home screen widgets for quick note access
•	Shared notes & collaboration tools

Developer’s Note
This release marks the beginning of a powerful, mobile-first productivity tool.


